cross: Phragmipedium Rosalie Dixler x Phragmipedium kovachii

measurements.description: One flower on one 19.2-cm inflorescence; dorsal sepal dark maroon. lighter distally; synsepal very pale green; petals slightly reflexed, dark maroon, lighter appearing areas proximally; pouch intense dark maroon, interior cream spotted maroon; pollen cap cream dusted maroon; substance medium; texture velvet.
